Package: nmar
Type: Package
Title: Not Missing at Random
Version: 0.0.0.9
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jane", "Doe",
      email = "jane@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Tools for estimation under Not Missing at Random (NMAR)
    mechanisms, including an empirical likelihood (EL) estimator for
    population means with optional auxiliary moment constraints. Supports
    both data frame and complex survey designs, with delta or bootstrap
    variance estimation and rich diagnostics.
